- page_title << "IP Reputation"

.pageHeader
  %h1.pageHeader__title IP Reputation Management

.pageContent.pageContent--compact

  %p.pageContent__intro.u-margin
    Manage and monitor the reputation of your IP addresses. Track blacklistings,
    warmup progress, and health metrics across all your mail servers.

  %ul.largeList.u-margin
    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to dashboard_ip_reputation_index_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong Dashboard
        %p.largeList__subText View overall statistics, recent blacklist events, and health actions

    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to health_ip_reputation_index_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong IP Health Status
        %p.largeList__subText Monitor reputation scores and health status for all IP addresses

    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to trends_ip_reputation_index_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong Historical Trends
        %p.largeList__subText View reputation trends and metrics over time

    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to ip_blacklist_records_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong Blacklist Records
        %p.largeList__subText View and manage detected blacklist events

    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to ip_domain_exclusions_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong Domain Exclusions & Warmup
        %p.largeList__subText Manage paused IPs and warmup progress for specific domains

    %li.largeList__item
      = link_to ip_health_actions_path, :class => 'largeList__link' do
        %strong Health Actions Audit Log
        %p.largeList__subText View complete history of all health actions (automatic and manual)

  .buttonSet.u-margin
    = link_to "Go to Dashboard", dashboard_ip_reputation_index_path, :class => "button button--positive"
